- don't rinse mushrooms, wipe wih damp cloth to clean

[ spice mix ]
- salt
- white & black pepper (1:2)
- paprika
# - ground fennel seed
# - five spice

[ dry batter ]
- add flour and spice mix to a bowl
- ratios
    -  200g :  8g  :     3g     :   3g   
    - flour : salt : pepper mix : paprika

[ wet batter ]
- combine dry batter and water in a 4:9 ratio
    - i.e. dry batter weight * 9/4 = wet batter weight

[ prepping ]
- chop oysters into thin tenders
- double coat (i.e. dry -> wet -> dry -> wet) with batter

[ cooking ]
- fry at 175Â°C
